Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.98,0:22:25.53,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}晨曦的光芒太过耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.99,0:22:31.49,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}令人不禁想要放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.83,0:22:37.54,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}坦露自己的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.87,0:22:42.42,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}任凭此身沉浮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.04,0:22:45.88,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}你握紧冰冷的十指
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.88,0:22:48.76,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}脸上是悲切的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.76,0:22:51.72,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我无言以对
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.93,0:22:54.68,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}只有视野渐渐模糊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.85,0:22:57.64,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}不需言语粉饰
