Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（OP）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.43,0:01:41.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一大早又戴着奇怪的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.04,0:01:43.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说过多少次让你别玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.12,0:01:48.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是不这么做我干劲就上不来嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.09,0:01:51.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那些干劲都不知道拿去做什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.72,0:02:03.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小楯 真壁司令来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.76,0:02:04.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真壁？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.52,0:02:07.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 决定了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.00,0:02:08.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.96,0:02:10.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,近藤剑司要驾驶Mk.Ⅷ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.36,0:02:14.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小楯卫要驾驶Mk.Ⅴ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.63,0:02:16.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己的儿子和女人跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.93,0:02:19.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就让别人的儿子来开法芙娜是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.63,0:02:21.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真壁司令不是那样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.34,0:02:25.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你女儿不用开 所以你才说得出这种话！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.41,0:02:30.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.31,0:02:33.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明已经做好心理准备了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.60,0:02:35.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.Ⅵ和Mk.Ⅳ报销了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.53,0:02:38.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光靠Mk.Ⅲ确实是不够啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.87,0:02:41.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒也是个机会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.36,0:02:45.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能让我反省反省自己这个当爹的一直以来都为他做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.63,0:02:50.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的命就交给你和总士了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.06,0:02:53.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要把他活着还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.22,0:02:57.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我保证
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.60,0:03:08.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翔子 听说近藤和小楯要去驾驶法芙娜了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.33,0:03:13.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是只有我什么都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.18,0:03:15.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能眼睁睁看着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.91,0:03:20.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翔子你以前也是这样的心情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.62,0:03:25.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每当我把学校的照片拿给你看的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.89,0:03:27.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都是这样寂寞的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.70,0:03:38.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然到了现在才终于理解你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.86,0:03:45.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也没资格教训一骑和皆城呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.83,0:03:51.37,title1,NTP,0,0,200,,{\fad(500,500)}第12回
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.45,0:03:51.37,title2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur35\t(0,600,\blur0)\fad(0,500)}不　　　　在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.54,0:03:51.37,title3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,1000)\fad(300,500)}焦 躁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.70,0:03:51.37,loc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}龙宫岛坐标：北纬11°31′37″ 东经145°04′36″
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.75,0:03:54.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 我要当驾驶员？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:55.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.62,0:03:57.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 说是确定了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.13,0:04:00.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剑司
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.44,0:04:03.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是不愿意 妈妈就去帮你说…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:04.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.96,0:04:05.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.73,0:04:07.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能靠这个去泡妞了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.43,0:04:08.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.20,0:04:11.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这笨儿子！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.38,0:04:35.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老公 今天就先休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.84,0:04:38.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天也因为给法芙娜做调整都没合眼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.67,0:04:40.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我这当爹的必须要做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.12,0:04:44.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.98,0:04:46.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么需要尽管说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.79,0:04:48.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.83,0:04:58.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俘虏 吃饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.10,0:05:05.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这种人为什么能成为神剑型的驾驶员？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.56,0:05:06.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.68,0:05:11.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会在战斗中怯场 被我砍断手的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.53,0:05:12.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.86,0:05:19.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你是那部红色机体的驾驶员？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.73,0:05:20.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.27,0:05:23.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那部机体归我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.63,0:05:25.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经没用了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.96,0:05:26.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.57,0:05:32.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都是人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.18,0:05:34.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然还能面不改色地战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.78,0:05:36.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定不正常
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.45,0:05:42.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快把我放出去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.48,0:05:43.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这种小丫头片子…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.36,0:05:46.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我开门！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.96,0:05:50.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的指挥官是谁 马上把他叫来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.75,0:05:52.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然敢这么对我 你们知道会有什么后果吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.38,0:05:54.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快给我开门！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.93,0:06:00.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面命令我 不消停点就这么对付你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.47,0:06:06.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 新联合国那边联系过你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.58,0:06:07.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.42,0:06:08.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.04,0:06:13.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但愿一骑他们没半路碰上祝福者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.46,0:06:20.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦结个账
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.11,0:06:22.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 保
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.66,0:06:25.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原稿我存到13号磁盘的文件夹里了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.06,0:06:28.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 正在确认
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.00,0:06:30.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上就交到印刷部去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.29,0:06:32.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.86,0:06:37.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 你最近这么忙还画了这么多页啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.73,0:06:41.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是在为梦想战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.63,0:06:46.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H827272&\bord0\frz338.2\pos(702,884)}我们是在\N为梦想战斗!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.45,0:06:43.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是理所当然的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.05,0:06:46.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这上面写着一样的台词呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.18,0:06:49.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不是么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.34,0:06:50.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.67,0:06:53.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,送你一瓶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.88,0:06:55.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢了 大婶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.02,0:07:00.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汇报情况！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.86,0:07:04.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,4点钟方向 距离785单位处出现重力反应
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.54,0:07:09.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标 我看看…正以航向740靠近本岛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.08,0:07:12.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所罗门发出应答 判断为质问者型
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.12,0:07:15.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剑司…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.74,0:07:25.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和以往的不一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.78,0:07:28.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法芙娜以三机阵形展开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.78,0:07:28.29,ruby,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(776,1000)}triple dog
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.03,0:07:30.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用蝠鲼运输机搭载机体
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.03,0:07:30.17,ruby,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(556,1000)}Devil Ray
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.03,0:07:30.17,tips,NTP,0,0,0,,注：蝠鲼 生活在海中 具有翼状胸鳍的软骨鱼类
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.47,0:07:32.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他们在敌人前进路线上的陆地进行迎击
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.16,0:07:35.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不由布伦希尔德系统辅助吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.78,0:07:39.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 敌人现在还没有接近龙宫岛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.88,0:07:41.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和之前的好像不太一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.19,0:07:42.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.16,0:07:43.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动作快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.10,0:07:45.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,20秒之内完成换装
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.13,0:07:47.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要装到蝠鲼运输机上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.04,0:07:49.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,移出机架的检查也别忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.09,0:07:50.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.49,0:07:58.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你了 要把孩子们平安无事地带回来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.91,0:08:05.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去跟卫说 那个不适合他啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.86,0:08:07.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说了也白说啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.39,0:08:11.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在这方面是顽固透顶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.34,0:08:20.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这打扮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.73,0:08:21.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 卫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.17,0:08:23.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是男人的初战
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.93,0:08:24.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.90,0:08:26.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小楯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.06,0:08:32.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.76,0:08:35.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.67,0:08:39.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三部法芙娜由蝠鲼运输机搭载
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.85,0:08:40.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前往目的地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.55,0:08:42.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在与敌人接触之前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.94,0:08:46.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由Mk.Ⅴ带头降落 展开三机阵形
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.84,0:08:49.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总士 我的行动代号是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.88,0:08:50.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高帕！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.76,0:08:55.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法芙娜Mk.Ⅴ 移出机架
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.53,0:08:59.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高帕！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.18,0:09:13.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蝠鲼运输机 起飞准备就绪 没有异常
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.65,0:09:16.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们俩没有做过意识改变状态测试
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.08,0:09:18.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能通过协同代码的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.00,0:09:22.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来预测他们的精神是否会发生改变吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.46,0:09:28.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咲良的意识在上次出击时变得极具攻击性
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.49,0:09:31.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他两人应该也会发生变化
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.87,0:09:32.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,线路畅通
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.59,0:09:34.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注意驾驶员的精神变化
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.10,0:09:36.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.25,0:09:40.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是一骑的话 就不会有这种问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.56,0:09:42.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蝠鲼运输机 起飞
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(Part-b)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.31,0:10:03.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两分钟后将到达目标群岛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.16,0:10:06.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各自在射出后4秒之内启动推进器
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.95,0:10:08.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,移动到预定位置待命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.58,0:10:11.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在收到命令之前千万不要动手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.39,0:10:14.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪 在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.17,0:10:19.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蝠鲼运输机 前方20公里处出现引力子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.25,0:10:21.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去会正面撞上的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.34,0:10:24.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紧急脱离 切断吊箱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.37,0:10:32.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第1重力波防护罩受到攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.80,0:10:35.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远程攻击型的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.36,0:10:43.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不玩了 妈妈 我想回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.68,0:10:45.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死的祝福者！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.02,0:10:47.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来得正好！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.34,0:10:55.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认法芙娜已落地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.12,0:10:58.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各驾驶员的生命体征显示到屏幕上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.19,0:11:04.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驾驶员的精神状态果然发生了很大的改变
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.28,0:11:06.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.63,0:11:08.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人先主动亮招数了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.11,0:11:10.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经确认到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.68,0:11:13.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会依据这些情报重新制定战术
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.54,0:11:15.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卫 你要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.81,0:11:21.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总士 咲良 剑司
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.48,0:11:23.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说 我有个主意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.40,0:11:25.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.59,0:11:26.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 Mk.Ⅴ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.70,0:11:30.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是…高帕！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.08,0:11:33.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我故意让敌人打中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.03,0:11:36.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剑司和咲良就趁这个机会打倒敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.78,0:11:37.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.78,0:11:40.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事真的能行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.61,0:11:42.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能打倒敌人 要怎么做都行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.67,0:11:43.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点让我战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.68,0:11:45.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 Mk.Ⅴ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.41,0:11:49.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的埃癸斯护盾如果没能完全防住敌人的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.41,0:11:49.96,ruby,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(366,1000)}Aegis
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.41,0:11:49.96,tips,NTP,0,0,0,,注：埃癸斯 希腊神话中的神盾 相传宙斯和雅典娜各有一面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.37,0:11:52.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么大家都会陷入险境
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.32,0:11:54.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算胜利的几率是0%
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.96,0:11:57.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也要相信明天的太阳去战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.65,0:11:59.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是机动武士！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.44,0:12:01.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乱七八糟…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.94,0:12:04.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.04,0:12:06.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则我就把你们全都从驾驶座里打出来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.40,0:12:08.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这战术不赖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:10.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他们试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.45,0:12:11.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.57,0:12:12.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们的精神出现了变化
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.43,0:12:16.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就当作是卫处在了原本应该由咲良所处的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.62,0:12:21.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想一想有什么能让装备埃癸斯护盾的人打头阵的战术
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.03,0:12:24.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人用的是远程直线攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.75,0:12:27.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.Ⅴ应对它是绰绰有余
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.12,0:12:31.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在你要相信驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.34,0:12:32.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.68,0:12:36.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标正向法芙娜降落地点移动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.95,0:12:44.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第1重力波防护罩 消失！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.98,0:12:46.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法芙娜全机散开
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.48,0:12:49.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在敌人发动攻击的同时
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.02,0:12:52.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.Ⅷ从3点钟方向开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.94,0:12:55.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.Ⅲ趁机抄到敌人后方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.37,0:13:00.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.12,0:13:03.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是现在！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.05,0:13:04.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.90,0:13:11.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.53,0:13:20.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.31,0:13:51.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高帕大投！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.31,0:13:51.07,ruby,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(746,1000)}smash
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.39,0:14:02.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认敌人已被消灭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.00,0:14:04.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驾驶员都平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.44,0:14:08.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咲良…还好你没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.54,0:14:14.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得漂亮 笨儿子…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.00,0:14:19.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.04,0:14:25.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在拼命战斗 我却…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.34,0:14:31.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老公 卫他 卫他…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.59,0:14:32.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.55,0:14:34.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得漂亮啊 老大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.98,0:14:36.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 干得漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.39,0:14:39.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卫那小子 干得漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.94,0:14:42.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都没事真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.50,0:14:46.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 在羽佐间你面前这么高兴…真是对不住
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.05,0:14:50.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我也真的很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.67,0:14:52.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请好好夸奖卫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.74,0:14:55.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.89,0:15:00.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么非得进这种地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.99,0:15:02.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可是保护了岛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.74,0:15:05.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你们自作主张的惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.33,0:15:07.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在里面醒醒脑子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.32,0:15:10.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总士说得没错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.80,0:15:13.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卫 你还戴着那东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.03,0:15:18.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是因为你射击太烂了总士才会不满意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.34,0:15:19.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好反省一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.58,0:15:20.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 卫…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.90,0:15:23.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是 动作再快点 乌龟…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.67,0:15:25.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛痛痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.07,0:15:31.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…我们怎么会在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.47,0:15:36.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们怎么都这么凶啊 好讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.00,0:15:38.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.86,0:15:38.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混帐！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.36,0:15:39.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.50,0:15:41.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说什么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.44,0:15:45.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随着协同代码的形成
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.64,0:15:47.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个人的精神都会产生显著的变化
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.67,0:15:51.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羽佐间和春日井就有这样的征兆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.29,0:15:54.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过 没想到会变化得如此剧烈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.46,0:16:01.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后在出击时也必须考虑到他们的意识改变状态才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.85,0:16:02.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.73,0:16:05.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑为什么不会发生改变呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.20,0:16:08.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与法芙娜融为一体所需要的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.66,0:16:12.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是遗传上的特质与积极的自我否定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.18,0:16:16.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤其是后者极大地影响着驾驶时的意识改变状态
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.11,0:16:20.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您的意思是因为一骑平时就一直在否定自己
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:23.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以驾驶法芙娜时心态也不会改变吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.46,0:16:25.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.39,0:16:27.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.87,0:16:32.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的精神之所以能维持稳定 是因为你在他的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.83,0:16:36.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要稳定的…是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.71,0:16:40.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一点一骑也是明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.16,0:16:43.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.96,0:16:46.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我就先告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.21,0:16:52.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑为什么出走 你有头绪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.16,0:16:54.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.23,0:16:57.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,积极的自我否定前方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.25,0:16:59.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是绝对的肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.82,0:17:04.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你和一骑有朝一日能到达那里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.56,0:17:10.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这话说得 就像一骑还在岛上一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.71,0:17:13.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.61,0:17:16.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没指望他会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.38,0:17:23.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,入夜之前我会放他们三个出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.18,0:17:26.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他们的父母也正急着想见自己的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.73,0:17:28.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.59,0:17:33.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学会了对对方抱以敬意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.81,0:17:36.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果使彼此渐行渐远了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.19,0:17:41.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一点和过去的皆城很像
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.98,0:17:46.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我家那笨儿子这会儿估计已经是人类军的阶下囚了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.11,0:17:51.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然觉得这样比驾驶法芙娜战斗要好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.04,0:17:54.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许我不配做司令啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.84,0:18:16.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆城
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.33,0:18:20.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑那边还是没有消息吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.12,0:18:24.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 也有可能被祝福者袭击了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.95,0:18:26.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者被新联合国抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.34,0:18:29.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是怎样 都与我无关
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.72,0:18:31.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.87,0:18:33.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他没有体谅你？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.06,0:18:36.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有试着去体谅他吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.98,0:18:38.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他我是理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.16,0:18:40.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通过齐格飞系统
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.28,0:18:46.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无数次和他共享过感情 深层心理和战斗时的思维
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.31,0:18:50.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用机器来窥探人心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.48,0:18:53.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这能算得上是理解吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.29,0:18:57.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底理解一骑什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.96,0:19:01.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少比你理解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.99,0:19:05.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.13,0:19:09.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是个拖后腿的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.71,0:19:13.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在CDC也没帮上什么忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.34,0:19:16.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法芙娜也开不了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.70,0:19:17.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这还不止
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.88,0:19:21.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着大家拼命战斗 我竟然还很羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.44,0:19:26.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么都不明白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.11,0:19:29.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.18,0:19:30.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.40,0:19:32.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.14,0:19:36.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在没必要战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.31,0:19:40.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.78,0:19:42.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆城
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.98,0:19:44.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.67,0:19:50.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这句话 为什么不对一骑也说？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.77,0:19:53.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是能说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.63,0:19:55.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早就说了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.49,0:20:01.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 好久不见 真壁一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.43,0:20:03.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,房间太小不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.31,0:20:05.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要到外面透透气？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.73,0:20:08.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,道生哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.99,0:20:16.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是 你是第一次出岛？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.27,0:20:16.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.92,0:20:17.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 对了对了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.53,0:20:21.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别怨我 这也是规定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.48,0:20:22.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.62,0:20:25.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就快到摩尔多瓦了 在那之前就忍一忍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.96,0:20:26.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.04,0:20:30.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 道生哥你现在住在哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.94,0:20:34.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有固定的住处
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.58,0:20:37.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五年前老爸带我出岛以后
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.78,0:20:41.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就成了人类军的士兵 到处出任务
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.89,0:20:44.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类军的士兵？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.88,0:20:47.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 能跟我说说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.28,0:20:49.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙宫岛的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.86,0:20:52.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.29,0:20:54.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我妈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.70,0:20:57.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个 我听说祝福者第一次出现的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.01,0:21:01.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她和藏前一起…被同化了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.25,0:21:07.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该不该告诉老爸呢 真为难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.33,0:21:13.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.55,0:21:16.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远见弓子…现在怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.62,0:21:17.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弓子姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.96,0:21:19.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她现在是学校保健室的老师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.91,0:21:21.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她当了老师？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.99,0:21:23.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.08,0:21:27.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她以前的梦想是去东京当偶像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.72,0:21:28.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.90,0:21:29.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,666
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.77,0:21:32.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,666？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.14,0:21:34.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的代号
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.37,0:21:36.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说卡农
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.92,0:21:40.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待命的时候就别这么死板了 叫名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.10,0:21:42.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我的上司
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.45,0:21:45.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能叫上司的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.60,0:21:47.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个死脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.09,0:21:49.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一骑 这家伙叫卡农
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.46,0:21:52.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是砍了你的法芙娜的手的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.48,0:21:55.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道 刚才她说过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.18,0:21:59.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 卡农主动跟人说话还真是少见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.10,0:22:01.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对一骑很在意吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.12,0:22:02.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不会
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.50,0:22:04.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 我们到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.40,0:22:08.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是…！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.68,0:22:11.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新联合国 人类军摩尔多瓦基地
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（ED）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.21,0:23:24.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.37,0:23:27.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被侵蚀的现在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.77,0:23:31.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与过去的联系
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.17,0:23:34.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,存在于未来的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.63,0:23:37.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是新的岔路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.68,0:23:43.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 苍穹的法芙娜 第十三回
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.38,0:23:45.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,侵蚀 -祝福者-
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.90,0:23:49.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在那里吗
